Buck Young https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buck_Young 0 David Darnell Brown (born March 15, 1981), best known by his stage name Young Buck, is an American rapper. Buck is a former member of the hip hop group UTP Playas. As a music executive, he heads his own record label, Cashville Records, and is currently a member of the hip hop group G-Unit.
